<h1>Alert: Your Website Is Down</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.email %>,</p>

<p>
  We attempted to reach your website: <strong><%= @website.url %></strong>, but it responded with status code <strong><%= @response.status_code %></strong> at <%= @response.created_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M") %>.
</p>

<% if @response.error.present? %>
  <p>Error details: <%= @response.error %></p>
<% end %>

<p>Please investigate the issue. We’ll continue monitoring and let you know of any changes.</p>

<p>– Ping Empire</p>
